#5296 

When we set referenceCofnig.setGeneric("protobuf-json") , and this property will be replaced by "true"
as this method "ReferenceConfig.class.getMethods" put  "getGeneric()" method in front of "isGeneric()" method. 

## Root Cause
![method invoke track](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/12695349/68477206-cd736400-0267-11ea-94aa-0de0a151a521.png)
When referenceConfig want to merge configs, tt change reference config property to parameter map.
In case of generic property ,it has two "get" methods, 
```
    @Parameter(excluded = true)
    public Boolean isGeneric() {
        return this.generic != null ? ProtocolUtils.isGeneric(generic) : null;
    }
public String getGeneric() {
        return generic;
    }
```
when we use org.apache.dubbo.config.AbstractConfig#getMetaData to get property map.The last one method will overwrite the first one.The "protobuf-json" be set to "true".

Some Test Code
```
import java.lang.reflect.Method;
import java.util.Arrays;

import org.apache.dubbo.config.ReferenceConfig;
public class MainClass {
  public static void main(String[] args) {
    Method[] methods = ReferenceConfig.class.getMethods();
    Arrays.stream(methods).forEach(System.out::println);
  }
}
```
the order of method will be different in different operation system. 

